WEBVTT

00:12:29.541 --> 00:12:33.461
If we are able to fulfill that promise,

00:12:33.485 --> 00:12:37.718
I believe we can create a bold
and brilliant world

00:12:37.742 --> 00:12:41.191
where future generations are able to form

00:12:41.215 --> 00:12:46.945
the same relationship to water
that we have been privileged to have,

00:12:48.460 --> 00:12:53.777
where all communities
of human and nonhuman relations

00:12:53.801 --> 00:12:56.093
have water to live,

00:12:56.117 --> 00:12:58.262
because water is life.

00:12:58.966 --> 00:13:00.429
Tabutni. Thank you.